prodtype: rhel7,fedora

title: 'Enable rsyslog Service'

description: |-
    The <tt>rsyslog</tt> service provides syslog-style logging by default on Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.
    <systemd-service-macro enable="true" service="rsyslog" />

rationale: |-
    The <tt>rsyslog</tt> service must be running in order to provide
    logging services, which are essential to system administration.

severity: medium

